From: Chad Monroe <chad@monroe.io>
Date: Wed, 25 Mar 2026 18:50:40 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] mt76: don't force survey update in mt76_get_survey()

All drivers already refresh survey data every 100-250ms via mac_work.

Signed-off-by: Chad Monroe <chad@monroe.io>
---
 mac80211.c |    3 ---
 1 file changed, 3 deletions(-)

--- a/mac80211.c
+++ b/mac80211.c
@@ -1133,9 +1133,6 @@ int mt76_get_survey(struct ieee80211_hw
 
 		sband = mt76_get_survey_sband(phy, &idx);
 
-		if (idx == 0 && phy->dev->drv->update_survey)
-			mt76_update_survey(phy);
-
 		if (sband || !hw->wiphy->n_radio)
 			break;
 	}
